多件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e5789c0d5e05ec0aa7ef79cabf729042c076a1","tid":803928,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5751ccc1ea2f02856d9798eaadf1f23e64e7ac1","tid":803928,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00e036a65e0363b9c9a8f984cc5fb803ec0c9b86","tid":803928,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d9aee7f5f1d6839c9044a50a9396e9190b7742dc","tid":803928,"uid":9104,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"F-35已經擁有了高達6000架的訂單<br />\n哇六千架 幾多萬億生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"F-35A：8900萬美元 <br />\nF-35B：1.228億美元<br />\nF-35C：1.218億美元<br />\n<br />\n加埋d training,保養維修，閒時系統升級 fatfat"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"有冇 6000架咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:20:12.000Z","msg":"6000架分15年<br />\n每年400億美元進帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761eef4d3aeb076444ba519e2b62fdfcd31b9e72","tid":803928,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> FYI:<br />\n中國軍火遭退貨，巴鐵購買土耳其直升機，理由令我國頗為無奈<br />\n<br />\n近日巴基斯坦和土耳其經過了多次的談判最終簽訂了軍火訂單，也就意味著我國的武直-10直升機將會遭到巴鐵的退貨，選擇購買土耳其的T-129直升機。而巴鐵給出的理由也讓我國十分的無奈，巴基斯坦軍方負責人聲稱目前巴基斯坦的空軍還不需要裝備我國的武直-10，購買直升機僅僅是用來驅趕國內的武裝分子，而並不需要直升機具備發裝甲能力。而我國研發的武直-10最大的亮點就是反裝甲能力。雖然我國出口給巴鐵的武直-10價格並不貴但是還是遭到了拒絕。直接將十多億的軍火訂單交給了土耳其。這讓土耳其的軍火公司十分的開心，隨後就在武器，配件和日常維護以及人員培訓上給出了巨大的優惠，甚至提出會在巴基斯坦境內建立一個生產線。在土耳其巨大的誘惑下巴鐵選擇了購買其生產的T-129直升機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外界認為巴基斯坦之所以選擇土耳其的T-129直升機並不是完全沒有道理的，首先土耳其從直升機的彈藥油料以後期維護上給出了優惠，再加上為其免費培訓飛行員和在巴基斯坦建立生產線，從長遠上來看對巴基斯坦來說是非常划算的。其次這次軍火合同的總金額為十五億美元，對土耳其來說是軍火銷售歷史上最大的一筆訂單。因為巴基斯坦每年的軍費支出僅僅只有九十億美元，所以只能選擇比較便宜的武器裝備，最重要的是土耳其生產的T-129直升機可以和巴基斯坦目前裝備的AH-1Z直升機通用發動機，這才後期的維護和日常保養上會大大的節省一筆費用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/world/j4kvqry.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fworld%2Fj4kvqry.html&d=T9g%2FiA0Nbt%2BmJ4ifiaHkZAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=77b65399\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/world/j4kvqry.html</a>"},{"pid":"186d87e43f38df07920afec2f5f1d1cbda6c4d6e","tid":803928,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"其他理由:<br />\n<a href=\"https://jmqmil.sina.cn/wqzb/doc-ihfqtahi8239456.d.html?cre=tianyi&amp;mod=wpage&amp;loc=7&amp;r=32&amp;doct=0&amp;rfunc=14&amp;tj=none&amp;tr=32\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjmqmil.sina.cn%2Fwqzb%2Fdoc-ihfqtahi8239456.d.html%3Fcre%3Dtianyi%26mod%3Dwpage%26loc%3D7%26r%3D32%26doct%3D0%26rfunc%3D14%26tj%3Dnone%26tr%3D32&d=T9g%2FiA0Nbt%2BmJ4ifiaHkZAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=0f477f1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://jmqmil.sina.cn/wqzb/doc-ihfqtahi8239456.d.html?cre=tianyi&amp;mod=wpage&amp;loc=7&amp;r=32&amp;doct=0&amp;rfunc=14&amp;tj=none&amp;tr=32</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/41467998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F41467998&d=T9g%2FiA0Nbt%2BmJ4ifiaHkZAEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=ad4902fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/41467998</a><br />\n<br />\n賣得成先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef89ca42ee95fb18cdd4303c870f81f2493d8169","tid":803928,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"畀以色列練兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />